# Pricing {#pricing route=/pricing layout=marketing}

Simple plans for small teams.

<!-- @meta component=PlanList source=plans -->
## Plans

- Starter: $19
- Pro: $49

```yaml @id=plans-data
plans:
  - id: starter
    price: 19
  - id: pro
    price: 49
```

[contentDocument, contentCurrentSection, contentSection, contentData, contentPlainText](std/content.ssc)

```scalascript
val documentContent = contentDocument()
val plans = contentSection("plans").get
val here = contentCurrentSection()
val data = contentData("plans-data")

println(documentContent.title.getOrElse(""))
println(plans.title)
println(contentPlainText(plans))
println(data.isDefined.toString)
println(here.id)
```
